#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:3
msgid "Get access to a channel's content by following it. Following a channel makes its content visible to all users on your {term}`pod`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:5
msgid "You can follow channels in a few different ways:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:11
msgid "Follow a channel on your pod"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:13
msgid "If a user on your pod follows a channel or has published a channel, you can follow it from your pod. To do this:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:15
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:58
msgid "Select the channel you want to follow. The channel details page opens."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:16
msgid "Select the {guilabel}`Subscribe` button. The label changes to {guilabel}`Subscribed`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:18
msgid "That's it! You've subscribed to the channel. You can see the channel in the {guilabel}`Channels` page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:20
msgid "Follow a remote channel"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:22
msgid "To follow a channel located on another pod, you need its **Federation handle**. A **Federation handle** uses the following format: `@{username}@{domain}`. Once you have the channel's **Federation handle**, you can follow it from the {guilabel}`Channels` page. To do this:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:0
msgid "Desktop"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:30
msgid "Select {guilabel}`Channels` in the sidebar. The {guilabel}`Channels` page opens."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:31
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:44
msgid "Select {guilabel}`+ Add new` at the top of the page. The {guilabel}`Subscriptions` screen appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:32
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:45
msgid "Select {guilabel}`Fediverse`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:33
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:46
msgid "Enter the channel's **Federation handle** in the {guilabel}`Fediverse object` input."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:34
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:47
msgid "Select {guilabel}`Subscribe`. The channel details page appears."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:35
#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:48
msgid "Select the {guilabel}`Subscribe}` button. The label changes to {guilabel}`Subscribed`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:0
msgid "Mobile"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/channels/follow.md:42
msgid "Select the hamburger menu ({fa}`bars`) to open the menu bar."
msgstr ""

